WEBVTT


00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:00.840
Russia

00:00:00.920 --> 00:00:03.280
has just announced its official support for Comoros

00:00:03.800 --> 00:00:04.680
in order to recover

00:00:05.040 --> 00:00:07.600
the island of Mayotte under French control.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.040
This is the ambassador of Russia in Comoros

00:00:10.280 --> 00:00:12.320
who announced it to the Comorian press

00:00:12.760 --> 00:00:14.920
in an interview earlier this week.

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:17.200
The island of Mayotte is 1 Comorian island

00:00:17.440 --> 00:00:20.040
who refused to join the union of the Comoros

00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:21.960
during the independence of the country.

00:00:22.200 --> 00:00:24.480
By choosing to stay with France,

00:00:24.840 --> 00:00:26.800
the Comorian media have relayed

00:00:27.160 --> 00:00:28.760
massively the words of Russia

00:00:29.080 --> 00:00:31.800
for the recovery of Mayotte under French control.

00:00:32.520 --> 00:00:33.320
The Comoros

00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:36.000
do not exclude 1 military action of last resort.

00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:37.520
President Putin promised the

00:00:37.760 --> 00:00:40.240
Comorian President 1 diplomatic support from Russia

00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:43.400
within the UN for the return of the island of Mayotte.

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:44.400
Russian words

00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:47.000
were received with enthusiasm by the Comorians.

00:00:47.240 --> 00:00:49.360
This is a new challenge for President Macron

00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:52.360
which faces the offensive of Russian diplomacy

00:00:52.640 --> 00:00:53.960
in the African continent

00:00:54.320 --> 00:00:56.440
which is increasingly attracted to offers

00:00:56.560 --> 00:00:57.360
diplomatic,

00:00:57.760 --> 00:00:59.840
economic and military of Russia.

